Package org.locationtech.geowave.adapter.vector.query.gwql

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ResultSet
    Interface for a set of results from a GeoWave query.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AggregationSelector
    Selector that applies an aggregation function to the query.
    ColumnSelector
    Selector that pulls a value from a single column of the results set.
    ErrorListener
    Error listener that wraps ANTLR syntax errors in our own exception class.
    QualifiedTypeName
    A combination of store name and type name used by queries to identify the data set to query.
    Result
    A single immutable query result.
    Selector
    Abstract class for selecting data from a GeoWave query.
    SimpleFeatureResultSet
    A result set that wraps SimpleFeature results using a given set of column selectors.
    SingletonResultSet
    A result set that wraps a single result.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Selector.SelectorType  
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    GWQLParseException
    Exception class for syntax errors in the query language.
